{"tid":280081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（真識嘆）日本仔高速公路邊揸車 邊享受裸女口交","createTime":"2017-06-11T22:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T03:38:23.000Z","uid":41351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe8020721758eda2f658d36fb7147115b23aa73","tid":280081,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T22:22:09.000Z","msg":"竟然有人在高速公路上面搞這檔事！<br />\n日本網友「かむ」在《推特》分享照片指出，他開車行經高速公路的時候，竟然看到行駛在他右邊的車輛，車內排檔桿上吊著一件內褲，一位裸女躺在副駕駛座(日本右駕)，頭部不偏不倚就在男駕駛的雙腿間，幫忙含棒棒，讓他大驚「你們在衝三小！？」並補充說拍照時其實是第二次接近這輛車，所以就特別並行行走了一段時間，還說對方挺激烈的！<br />\n而網友看到這張照片後，紛紛留言「我怎麼都沒看過這種的」、「這是在拍A片嗎」、「沒拍影片喔」、「如果緊急煞車的話不就會咬斷了嗎」。（即時新聞<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2F&d=N8xYUS4A8HlYY7RRcLmgcP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b0687084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/</a><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/062203_a1a852f18b39245214227db899b21fb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F062203_a1a852f18b39245214227db899b21fb9.jpg&h=3d68bd97&s={SIZE}\" />international/20170611/1137557/<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/062017_9a23caeffbea9580525a12dbdddec430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F062017_9a23caeffbea9580525a12dbdddec430.jpg&h=24c2f82b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/062018_50e30d6bc40d73ebaf40f3e40d1386c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F062018_50e30d6bc40d73ebaf40f3e40d1386c1.jpg&h=a0c75e79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5969a0a9caaa52fb551606fc4902de5b3fa79f4","tid":280081,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T22:27:22.000Z","msg":"<i